S32 E38

TV-PG 41min | 2020

Saturdays 10/9c

A young woman vanished after a night out in Milwaukee in October 2013. Did a meeting set up on a dating app lead to the disappearance or was it someone she knew? "48 Hours" correspondent Peter Van Sant reports. Air Date: May 16, 2020
